node.text:
I never imagined my animations would help so many other businesses grow online. 

I’ve been an animator for over 10 years, working with big brands and motion picture studios in Hollywood. I’ve mastered the art of grabbing viewers attention and keeping them hooked on the big screen. 

Using 3D animations on marketing videos has proven to be an insanely effective way to boost engagement, get more leads and sales online. 

Attention spans are shorter than ever and brands have a hard time standing out on social media. 
Breakout Clips has a HUGE template library of animations from artists like myself. 

With the fast drag & drop editor, you can create viral marketing videos in under 30 seconds 🔥

Would love to know if this has helped your business too!
